## How to Use

This file is read by the n8n automation system. Follow the format exactly:

- **Tasks** start with `- [ ]` followed by `TASK-ID: Description`
- **Acceptance criteria** are indented under tasks with `- [ ]`
- Status markers: `[ ]` pending, `[/]` in progress, `[x]` complete, `[!]` blocked

